abstract: >
  This repository provides reproducible scripts and figures for constructing
  spatially coherent neuron density fields in 3D, 4D, and 5D using Simplex noise.
  The density fields are designed as heterogeneous substrates for neural field
  models, geometric learning frameworks, and brain-inspired computation, with
  smooth bounded gradients suitable for metric and geodesic constructions.
